Source.Name: retroarch
Source.Summary: RetroArch is the official reference frontend for the libretro API
Source.Description: RetroArch is the reference frontend for the libretro API. Popular examples of implementations for this API includes videogame system emulators and game engines, but also more generalized 3D programs.
